OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fdying out and some evening sunshine
OL,7,Fexpected, freshening southwesterly
OL,8,Fwinds. Clouding over with the risk of
OL,9,Fsome showers later in the night.
OL,10,FFeeling quite muggy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FAfter a cloudy start to the
OL,13,Fday it will be a bright day with just
OL,14,Fa scattering of showers by afternoon.
OL,15,FWarm.
